import React ,{useState}from 'react'; import SubMenu from './SubMenu'; const Header = () => { const [menu, setMenu] = useState() const handleMouseOver = (e) => { console.log(e.target.dataset.state) console.log(e.target.ariaExpanded) console.log(e.target.innerHTML) e.target.dataset.state = "open"; e.target.ariaExpanded= true; setMenu(e.target.innerHTML) }; const handleMouseOut = (e) => { console.log(e) e.target.dataset.state = "closed"; e.target.ariaExpanded= false; setMenu('No') }; return ( <> < header class = "font-[DunkinSans] h-[clamp(60px,6.284vw,92px)] sticky top-0 text-espresso md:px-[10px] z-[60] bg-[url('/resources/images/common/header_bg.png')] bg-bottom lg:shadow-[0_0_20px_0_rgba(29,7,0,0.3)]" >

  • DUNKIN'

) } export default Header
